   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": "## Input/Output Schema\n\n### `create_blast_db`\n\n#### Input (`CreateBlastDbInput`)\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| fasta | str | Path to the input FASTA file containing sequences to create a BLAST database from |\n\n#### Config (`CreateBlastDbConfig`)\n| Field | Type | Default | Description |\n|-------|------|---------|-------------|\n| dbtype | Literal[\"nucl\", \"prot\"] | \"nucl\" | Specifies the type of database to create: Nucleotide or Protein |\n| out_prefix | Optional[str] | None | File-path prefix for database files (default: FASTA stem) |\n| title | Optional[str] | None | Optional name for the database |\n| additional_params | Dict[str, str \\| int \\| float \\| bool] | {} | Extra flags for makeblastdb (e.g., parse_seqids, hash_index) |\n\n#### Output (`CreateBlastDbOutput`)\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| db_path | str | Path to the generated BLAST database |\n\n---\n\n### `local_blast`\n\n#### Input (`LocalBlastInput`)\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| query | str | Path to FASTA file containing a query sequence |\n\n#### Config (`LocalBlastConfig`)\n| Field | Type | Default | Description |\n|-------|------|---------|-------------|\n| program | Literal[\"blastn\", \"blastp\", \"blastx\", \"tblastn\", \"tblastx\"] | \"blastn\" | Select which BLAST program to use for the search |\n| local_db | str | *(required)* | Specifies a path to the local BLAST database to search against |\n| num_threads | int | 4 | Number of threads to use |\n| additional_params | Dict[str, str \\| int \\| float \\| bool] | {} | Additional parameters for BLAST command (e.g., outfmt, max_target_seqs, word_size) |\n\n#### Output (`BlastOutput`)\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| results_df | Optional[pd.DataFrame] | DataFrame with BLAST results (columns: qseqid, sseqid, pident, length, mismatch, gapopen, qstart, qend, sstart, send, evalue, bitscore) |\n| num_hits | int | Number of BLAST hits found |\n\n---\n\n### `online_blast`\n\n#### Input (`OnlineBlastInput`)\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| query | str | Query sequence or path to FASTA file containing a query sequence |\n\n#### Config (`OnlineBlastConfig`)\n| Field | Type | Default | Description |\n|-------|------|---------|-------------|\n| program | Literal[\"blastn\", \"blastp\", \"blastx\", \"tblastn\", \"tblastx\"] | \"blastn\" | Selects which BLAST program is utilized for the search |\n| database | Literal[\"nt\", \"nr\", \"refseq_rna\", \"refseq_protein\", \"swissprot\", \"pdb\", \"pataa\", \"patnt\"] | \"nt\" | Specifies the NCBI database to search |\n| additional_params | Dict[str, str \\| int \\| float \\| bool] | {} | Additional parameters for NCBIWWW.qblast (e.g., word_size, expect, matrix) |\n\n#### Output (`BlastOutput`)\n| Field | Type | Description |\n|-------|------|-------------|\n| results_df | Optional[pd.DataFrame] | DataFrame with BLAST results (columns: qseqid, sseqid, pident, length, mismatch, gapopen, qstart, qend, sstart, send, evalue, bitscore) |\n| num_hits | int | Number of BLAST hits found |",
   "metadata": {}
  },
